Title: Breitling Superocean Automatic 44 Outerknown
Body (HTML):
<sections><section id="1"><sectionTitle>Details</sectionTitle><sectionBody>•	Features a striking stainless-steel case with a ratcheted unidirectional bezel, a feature that allows divers to time their dives accurately. 
	•	The rugged NATO strap—a style originally introduced in the British Ministry of Defence Standard 66-15—is made of regenerated ECONYL® nylon. Straps are interchangeable and additional straps can be purchased separately. 
	•	The screwed stainless steel caseback is engraved with the Outerknown logo, and the strap is detailed with an OK embroidery. 
	•	The COSC-certified chronometer is water-resistant to 100 bar / 1000 meters, so it will more than meet the needs of any underwater adventure. 
	•	The watch is self-winding, powered by the Breitling Caliber 17, which offers a power reserve of about 38 hours. 
	•	Super-LumiNova® luminescent numerals, indexes, and hands. 
	•	Each watch is presented in packaging made entirely of recycled materials. 
	•	Available to U.S. customers only.</sectionBody></section><section id="2"><sectionTitle>Size & Fit</sectionTitle><sectionBody>Click buy for more sizing information.</sectionBody></section><section id="3"><sectionTitle>Shipping & Returns</sectionTitle><sectionBody>For all U.S. orders, we offer free standard shipping on orders over $100. Title: Woolaroo Trunks
Body (HTML):
<sections><section id="1"><sectionTitle>Details</sectionTitle><sectionBody>•	In our constant quest to push the limits of sustainable design and responsible innovation, we partnered with The Woolmark Company to make the first 100% Merino wool surf trunks!
	•	Made entirely out of nature's original performance fiber. Merino wool is naturally breathable and odor resistant, making it a great material for activewear.
	•	A throwback to the days when trunks were considered equipment—they had to last, and stand up to monster waves and the nomadic lifestyle of a surfer.
	•	This trunk is for a man with a keen sense of nostalgia, who puts style and soul on the same plane as function and quality.
	•	Woolaroos are soft, yet strong—the more they get beat up, the better they look.
	•	These offer a superior drape, softness, durability, and quick-dry performance.
	•	Drawcord waistband with zip fly, and zip back pocket with bungee key ring.
	•	The Woolmark Company is the global authority on wool, with the The Woolmark logo being one of the world’s most recognized and respected textile brands in the world, representing excellence and innovation from farm to fashion.</sectionBody></section><section id="2"><sectionTitle>Size & Fit</sectionTitle><sectionBody>Click buy for more sizing information.</sectionBody></section><section id="3"><sectionTitle>Shipping & Returns</sectionTitle><sectionBody>For all U.S. orders, we offer free standard shipping on orders over $100.
